---
title: Coconut Courgette Curry with mushrooms and lemongrass rice
description: The gorgeous green courgette in this recipe is simmered and softened in a mild and creamy coconut curry sauce. Served with vibrant lemongrass rice and topped with crunchy cashews, this is a plant-based dish you won't want to miss!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W23_IE_IEXCVV0010-3_Main_high-9d63dc17.jpg
